  "expected_outcome": "ack_within_budget",
  "description": [
    "Phi master broadcasts an ANCHOR frame (TYPE=0x47) to all slaves.",
    "Slaves are required to ACK within 2 clock cycles of the SYNC_BURST.",
    "Wire C is open-drain wired-AND across slaves; pull-up returns it",
    "high only when all addressed slaves have released. Phi reads",
    "ACK-complete by sampling Wire C high after the strobe."
  ],
